This XAgent built-in Skill is adapted from document extraction and parsing workflow ideas in:
https://github.com/claude-office-skills/skills/tree/main/data-extractor
https://github.com/claude-office-skills/skills/tree/main/pdf-extraction
https://github.com/claude-office-skills/skills/tree/main/table-extractor

Only Markdown process guidance is bundled here. Upstream MCP declarations, office-mcp integration, parser library examples, OCR assumptions, Python code, and external command behavior are not bundled in this XAgent copy.

